---
import Mainlayout from '../layouts/Mainlayout.astro';

---
<Mainlayout title="Davis Doe's About"
seoTitle="About Davis, Software Engineer"
seoDesc={"Hi there! My name is Davis, and I'm a software engineer " +
  "with over 5 years of experience in the industry"}
>
<div class="w-6/12 mx-auto">
  <h1 class="text-5xl">About</h1>
  <img
    src="/public/images/s.jpg"
    class="my-5 shadow-md drop-shadow-[10px_10px_15px_rgba(49,125,31,9.6)]"
  />
  <p>
    Hi there! My name is Davis, and I'm a software engineer with over 5
    years of experience in the industry. I'm passionate about building
    high-quality software that solves real-world problems and makes people's
    lives easier.
  </p><br />
  <p>
    My expertise lies in full-stack development, with a focus on web
    applications. I'm proficient in a variety of programming languages,
    including JavaScript, Python, and Ruby, and I'm comfortable working with
    tools and frameworks like React, Node.js, and Django.
  </p><br />
  <p>
    In addition to my technical skills, I pride myself on my ability to
    collaborate with team members and communicate effectively with
    stakeholders. I'm a natural problem solver and enjoy tackling complex
    challenges.
  </p><br />
  <p>
    When I'm not coding, you can find me hiking in the mountains or playing
    guitar in my local band. I'm always looking for new opportunities to work
    on exciting projects, so if you're interested in collaborating, please
    feel free to get in touch. Thanks for stopping by!
  </p>
</div>
</Mainlayout>

